203
00:17:00,540 --> 00:17:03,970
Am I not allowed to be worried
if I can't spell that?

204
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:08,369
You've been fine for a while,
but you're getting arrogant again.

205
00:17:08,460 --> 00:17:11,410
