your credit card limit.

227
00:18:34,700 --> 00:18:37,340
-Yesterday, Seo-woo...
-Give it back.

228
00:18:38,300 --> 00:18:40,640
-What?
-If you need money, sell your car,

229
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:42,440
