on my best friend from someone else?

234
00:18:55,070 --> 00:18:56,480
You broke my heart.

235
00:18:57,750 --> 00:19:00,920
Soo-kyung, I'll tell you everything
once I figure out everything.

236
00:19:01,010 --> 00:19:02,860
